trans-unit.source: Provides parsing support for a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.StyleSheet" /> control.

trans-unit.source: The class object is internally created and used by the page parser when parsing the contents of a <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.StyleSheet> control.
trans-unit.target: O objeto da classe internamente é criado e usado pelo analisador de página ao analisar o conteúdo de um <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.StyleSheet> controle.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.StyleSheetControlBuilder> class recognizes inherited style classes.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.StyleSheetControlBuilder> classe reconhece classes de estilo herdado.
